      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with you today! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat about it!",
