    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example retains its factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and M Variable Differential Lock for precise power delivery. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains tight, delivering the communicative feedback and balanced weight distribution this chassis is renowned for. A driver-focused machine ready for the canyons.",
