    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as your favorite pair of jeans? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been a total gem! It runs beautifully and has been super well-loved, so it\u2019s in great shape and ready to hit the road with its next owner. Whether you're commuting or planning a weekend getaway, this beauty has got your back. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
