      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents a prime opportunity for the purist. At its heart lies the S54B32 engine, a masterpiece of engineering featuring a forged steel crankshaft and graphite-coated pistons. The dual-VANOS variable valve timing system ensures optimal torque delivery across the rev range, peaking at an exhilarating 8,000 RPM. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, providing direct mechanical engagement and power delivery to the rear-mounted variable M-differential lock. Recent technical highlights include a comprehensive cooling system overhaul, documented rear subframe reinforcement, and a precision valve shim adjustment. The MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension maintain excellent kinematic integrity. While the aesthetics show the honest patina of a driven car, the powertrain and chassis dynamics remain sharp and responsive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
